## 🔄 Client Crate Setup (Leptos Alternative)

**`client/Cargo.toml` (Leptos):**
```toml
[package]
name = "client"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
# Workspace
shared = { workspace = true }

# Leptos
leptos = { workspace = true }
leptos_axum = { workspace = true }
leptos_meta = { workspace = true }

# Utils
wasm-bindgen = "0.2"
console_log = "1.0"
log = "0.4"
```

**`client/src/main.rs` (Leptos):**
```rust
use leptos::*;
use leptos_axum::{generate_route_list, LeptosRoutes};
use leptos_meta::*;
use crate::pages::*;

#[component]
pub fn App() -> impl IntoView {
    provide_meta_context();

    view! {
        <Html lang="fr" />
        <Title text="Rust Full Stack" />
        <Router routes>
            <main>
                <Routes />
            </main>
        </Router>
    }
}

#[component]
fn HomePage() -> impl IntoView {
    view! {
        <h1>"Welcome to Leptos Full Stack"</h1>
        <p>"Axum backend + Leptos frontend + WasmGC"</p>
    }
}

#[component]
fn Counter() -> impl IntoView {
    let (count, set_count) = create_signal(0);
    let double = create_memo(move |_| count.get() * 2);

    view! {
        <button on:click=move |_| set_count.update(|n| *n += 1)>"+1"</button>
        <p>"Count: " {count}</p>
        <p>"Double: " {double}</p>
    }
}
```

