## 🔒 Environment Variables

**`.env.example`:**
```bash
# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://rustuser:rustpass@localhost:5432/rustfullstack

# Server
HOST=0.0.0.0
PORT=3000
RUST_LOG=info,tower_http=debug

# JWT
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-change-in-production
JWT_EXPIRATION=604800

# CORS
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:8080

# Redis (optional)
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
```

---

## 🚀 Development Workflow

```bash
# Start services
docker-compose up -d

# Run migrations
sqlx migrate run --source migrations

# Run server (Axum)
cd server && cargo run

# Run client (Dioxus with hot reload)
cd client && dx serve

# OR run fullstack (Dioxus handles both)
cd client && dx serve --fullstack

# Run tests
cargo test --workspace

# Run clippy
cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings

# Format code
cargo fmt --all

# Build for production
cargo build --release --workspace
```

